Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.79,0:00:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}早く食べたいよ～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}やっと みんなが
