Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}ほら タンバ ササゲ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}休憩は終わりだろ　店へ戻れ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}はい！　戻ろう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}-ほっ！\N-よっと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}うんしょ うんしょ\Nうんしょ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}あいつら 文句ばっかり
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}夕方の分のどら焼きは？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}ハッ！　今 出しまーす
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}うんしょっと…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}逃げようなんて考えたって\N無駄だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}よいしょ　ハッ
