Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}うん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.31,0:05:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}わあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}うわ～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}何度 見ても きれいだ～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&Hffffff&}うんしょ うんしょ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.42,0:05:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}うう…
